title: Have Mercy - acoustic blues rock [1977]
description:
Have Mercy was a natural, acoustic blues rock band. They played rocking harmonica blues with traditional instruments

Have Mercy:
Steve Baker [vocals, guitar, kazoo, harmonica]
Brian Barnett [vocals, dobro, slide and other guitars, kazoo]
Dick Bird [vocals, dobro and other guitars, mandolin, washboard]
Jon Echolls [vocals, harmonica, percussion]
Henry Heggen [lead vocals, harmonica, jug, washboard, megablaster]
Rory McLeod [lead vocals, harmonica, jug, washboard, spoons, bell, bassdrum]
Werner Weber [rhythm guitar on Dallas Rag]
